title: 2025 LACMA Art+Film Gala Photos: Angela Bassett, Demi Moore, Quinta Brunson and More Stars
summary: Ryan Coogler, Cynthia Erivo, Mary Corse, Emma Roberts, Demi Lovato, Elle Fanning, Kathryn Hahn, Ashley Park, Troye Sivan, Jon M. Chu, Tessa Thompson, Doja Cat, Paris Hilton and Lorde were also in attendance at the star-studded event.
